about.summary: A collection of robust statistical methods based on Wilcox' WRS functions. It implements robust t-tests (independent and dependent samples), robust ANOVA (including between-within subject designs), quantile ANOVA, robust correlation, robust mediation, and nonparametric ANCOVA models based on robust location measures.

name: r-wrs2
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '1.0-0' %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-wrs2
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/WRS2_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/WRS2/WRS2_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 1ac4b8292f142a8e9dde7755ce3734835f33eb0f379d5370acc581b720a3a7ab

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 2
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-mass
    - r-mc2d
    - r-plyr
    - r-reshape
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-mass
    - r-mc2d
    - r-plyr
    - r-reshape

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('WRS2')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('WRS2')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://r-forge.r-project.org/projects/psychor/
  license: GPL-3
  summary: A collection of robust statistical methods based on Wilcox' WRS functions. It implements
    robust t-tests (independent and dependent samples), robust ANOVA (including between-within
    subject designs), quantile ANOVA, robust correlation, robust mediation, and nonparametric
    ANCOVA models based on robust location measures.
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file: '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-3'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
